<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="K_5734" type="Brief"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>Andrea Podestà an Alfred Escher, Genua, Mittwoch, 01. Juni 1870</title></titleStmt><publicationStmt><p>Digitale Briefedition Alfred Escher, Zürich: Alfred Escher-Stiftung.</p></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><msDesc><msIdentifier><institution>SBB Historic</institution><idno>VGB_GB_SBBGB01_006</idno></msIdentifier></msDesc></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><textClass><keywords scheme="http://briefedition.alfred-escher.ch/keywords"><term>Gotthardbahnprojekt</term><term>Staatsverträge</term><term>Italienisches Parlament</term></keywords></textClass><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><persName key="Podestà Andrea" type="addressee">Andrea Podestà</persName><persName key="Escher (vom Glas) Alfred" type="sender">Alfred Escher</persName><placeName>Genua</placeName><date when="1870-06-01">01. Juni 1870</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><placeName>Zürich</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><ref type="previous" target="B5654"/><ref type="next" target="B3457"/><ref type="next-in-corresp" target="B5743"/><ref type="previous-in-corresp" target="B5741"/></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><front>
      
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_5734_p1"><lb xml:id="p1-l1"/>
          <hi rend="printed">CITTÀ DI <placeName key="Genua (I)">GENOVA</placeName> <lb xml:id="p1-l2"/>UFFIZIO
            DELLA SEGRETERIA <lb xml:id="p1-l3"/>Risposta alla Lettera <lb xml:id="p1-l4"/>del <add type="?"><choice><abbr>V.</abbr><expan>(Abkürzung nicht aufgelöst)</expan></choice></add> <lb xml:id="p1-l5"/><choice><abbr>N<hi rend="sup">o</hi> </abbr><expan>Numero (Nummer)</expan></choice> <lb xml:id="p1-l6"/>OGGETTO</hi>
        </p>
      
      <div type="dateline">
        <p rend="center" xml:id="K_5734_p2"><lb xml:id="p1-l7"/>
          <hi rend="printed">
            <placeName key="Genua (I)">Genova</placeName> addì</hi>
          <date when="1870-06-01">
            1<hi rend="sup">o</hi> Giugno <hi rend="printed">18</hi>70</date>
        </p>
      </div>
    </front><body>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5734_p3"><lb xml:id="p1-l8"/>Ricevo con molto piacere la notizia <lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>datami con di Lei
        telegramma d`<date when="1870-06-01">oggi</date> <lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>circa la imminente sanzione per
          <lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>parte del potere legislativo della <lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>Confederazione
        Elvetica delle <lb xml:id="p1-l13"/>convenzioni internazionali relative <lb xml:id="p1-l14"/>al <placeName key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">S. Gottardo</placeName>.</p>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5734_p4"><lb xml:id="p1-l15"/> Ho il miglior fondamento di <lb xml:id="p1-l16"/>sperare che fra pochi giorni
        il <lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>Governo <placeName key="Italien (Königreich)">Italiano</placeName>
        presenterà <lb xml:id="p1-l18"/>al Parlamento la proposta delle <lb xml:id="p1-l19"/>leggi
        necessarie per tradurre in <lb xml:id="p1-l20"/>atto l`opera di cui si tratta, <lb xml:id="p1-l21"/>e nella giornata d`<date when="1870-06-01">oggi</date> parto per <lb xml:id="p1-l22"/><placeName key="Florenz (I)">Firenze</placeName> dove mi occuperò di <lb xml:id="p1-l23"/>sollecitare con ogni mia possa <lb xml:id="p1-l24"/>una simile presentazione</p>
    </body><back>
      <div type="closer">
        <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_5734_p5"><lb xml:id="p1-l25"/>Col più distinto ossequio</p>
        <p rend="center" xml:id="K_5734_p6"><lb xml:id="p1-l26"/> Il Sindaco <lb xml:id="p1-l27"/>Presidente del Comitato <placeName key="Genua (I)">Genovese</placeName> per il Valico <placeName key="Alpen">Alpino</placeName> </p>
      </div>
      <div type="signature">
        <p rend="center" xml:id="K_5734_p7"><lb xml:id="p1-l28"/>A Podestà</p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_5734_p8"><lb xml:id="p1-l29"/>All`Illustrissimo<lb xml:id="p1-l30"/>
Signor Escher
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l31"/>Presidente del Comitato per la Ferrovia
        
<lb xml:id="p1-l32"/>del <placeName key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">Gottardo</placeName> <lb xml:id="p1-l33"/><placeName key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zurigo</placeName> </p>
      </div>
    </back></text></TEI>